bhop_citnez

Little map I have been working on and off on for about a month. When I started making this map I was planning to create a longer more technical map that would require good routing for a good run. It didn't quite end up how I hoped and ended up become more of a strafe style map. Intended to be about a minute or so but lost inspiration so I just decided to release it, map length is around 40-50 seconds. 

Hopefully my next map will be longer and more technical. I stream my mapping sometimes on twitch: twitch.tv/zenticbhop (shameless plug).

Enjoy! :)
